                      |YKBWelcome to Darkwind!|000

Most of the basic information about Darkwind can be found in the Newbie Tome.
You can obtain one from the Newbie Tome Dispenser at Center of Town. Use the
command |YKBncot|000 if you need to return there. Do not forget to look at the
machine, then |YKBpull lever|000 and |YKBread tome|000.

The following are basic directions to help you start your adventuring career.
This information can also be found in the Newbie Tome.

==============================================================================
Equipment, Stores and Bank
==============================================================================

Erga's newbie store.
Erga hands out free equipment that is perfectly suited for anyone under level
5. Do not waste your time looking elsewhere. He has some good quality stuff.

From Cot: w,w,w,w,s [4w,s]

Do not forget to read the sign.
______________________________________________________________________________

Donation room.
The mighty heroes and legendary adventurers that inhabit the realms of Darkwind
may be inclined to donate equipment to the more inexperienced adventurers.

You can visit the Donation room to see what they may have to offer you.

From Cot: n,n,n,n,n,e [5n,e]
______________________________________________________________________________

Bank.
You are able to keep your money safe at the bank. That way, if you die, you
will not lose your hard-earned cash.

From Cot: w,w,w,w,w,s,s,s,e [5w,3s,e]
______________________________________________________________________________

Taylors.
Taylors is the general store in town. He will be happy to buy your goods from
you. Selling treasures you find on your adventures is a great way to earn a
pretty penny.

From Cot: w,w,w,w,w,s,s,w [5w,2s,w]

