==============================================================================
Further Helpfiles of Interest
==============================================================================

help newbie
  The newbie command allows you to talk on the newbie channel.

help set
  The set command allows you to customize several different features.

help wimpy
  Wimpy allows you to automatically flee combat when your HP drop too low.

help mon
  The monitor allows you to set an HP/SP monitor.

help ncot - help npunch - help nkick - help nheal
  These are your newbie skills.

help combatbrief
  This setting allows you to filter your combat messages.

help score - help sc
  Information on your score tables.

help int - help wis - help dex - help con - help str - help chr
  Information about your stats.

help races
  Information on how to become one of the races that inhabit Darkwind.

help guilds
  A list of existing guilds on Darkwind. Specific info can be obtained from the
  tome.

help rules
  The rules for Darkwind. Read them, know them, live them.

help pk
  Information on Darkwind's player killing system.

